  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581120/extras/eb215d5fe4849867900eb68d566e73a0.webp?t=1742597663\" width=600 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581120/extras/26f1818b54e82e66c43df90caca35ae6.poster.avif?t=1742597663\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581120/extras/26f1818b54e82e66c43df90caca35ae6.webm?t=1742597663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Fight and lead your army from a ground level view of large fantasy battles, command your formation of troops, and direct your forces through hack-and-slash encounters to claim ultimate victory! Go head to head in objective based conquest mode. Test your defensive skills in a wave based survival mode, or employ grand strategy in a campaign mode. Varied troop types offer distinct fighting styles and weapons, allowing for diverse playstyles and tactics. Will you anchor a battle line with spearmen, shatter defenses with mighty great swords, or rain arrows upon your enemies? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581120/extras/9098fe32c022c73ed8201722c1931f10.webp?t=1742597663\" width=600 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581120/extras/43a26838dcdad13b68ebd7134214e636.poster.avif?t=1742597663\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581120/extras/43a26838dcdad13b68ebd7134214e636.webm?t=1742597663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Utilize the full roster of available troop loadouts to gain victory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Diverse Unit Arsenal:</strong> Command more than 70 troop types across 5 factions adding depth and dynamic strategies to class-based battles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strategic Formations:</strong> Employ formation tactics by adjusting your unit's stance and formation shape while also commanding your army as a whole.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wave Survival Siege Mode:</strong> Test your skills against increasing enemy pressure as you defend against waves of varied enemies. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiplayer Mayhem:</strong> Challenge your skills against AI bots or friends in local multiplayer.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Objective Based Gameplay:</strong> Battle for control of objectives and manipulate spawn points to strategically choose spawned allies.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581120/extras/6f8b7897913f492d4a351930bbcce614.webp?t=1742597663\" width=600 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581120/extras/2ebc4fc7a9130d17aae191e0654de5f1.poster.avif?t=1742597663\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581120/extras/2ebc4fc7a9130d17aae191e0654de5f1.webm?t=1742597663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Objective based gameplay where you capture objectives to drain your opponent's supplies and achieve victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581120/extras/df98ac039c05e26d124fc472b5e03e59.webp?t=1742597663\" width=600 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581120/extras/6d47a511e7547a5acb6970d2b09b3e36.poster.avif?t=1742597663\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581120/extras/6d47a511e7547a5acb6970d2b09b3e36.webm?t=1742597663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Defend your fortification against increasing waves of enemies to survive as long as possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581120/extras/2d1cc36947d465a8570c25b474481bf8.webp?t=1742597663\" width=600 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581120/extras/1e3cc8b31978a92f779bd34a6116ed61.poster.avif?t=1742597663\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2581120/extras/1e3cc8b31978a92f779bd34a6116ed61.webm?t=1742597663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Capture territories in an ongoing campaign to unlock additional unit types and clear your enemies from the region.</p>",
